{
  "text": "Are the seven archetypes for mind a function of or related to the seven densities that are to be experienced in the octave? I am Ra. The relationship is tangential in that no congruency may be seen. However, the progress through the archetypes has some of the characteristics of the progress through the densities. These relationships may be viewed without being, shall we say, pasted one upon the other.",
